value:
select 
cast(max_sid as integer) as max_sid ,
cast(branch_office_cd as varchar(10)) as branch_office_cd,
cast(branch_office_name as varchar(100)) as branch_office_name,
cast(branch_office_id as integer) as branch_office_id ,
cast(src_sys_cd as varchar(10)) as src_sys_cd,
cast(dim_region_key as integer) as dim_region_key,
cast(actv_rec_ind as varchar(1)) as actv_rec_ind,
etl_audit_id,
cast(branch_office_region_cd as varchar(10)) as branch_office_region_cd
from (
select 
LKP_MAXSID.MAX_SID AS MAX_SID,
src.* from (
select
NVL(stg_informeventas.branch_office_cd,0) as branch_office_cd ,
stg_informeventas.branch_office_name as branch_office_name,
null as branch_office_id,
'penta' as src_sys_cd,
null as dim_region_key,
'Y' as actv_rec_ind,
cast(0 as integer) as etl_audit_id,
null as branch_office_region_cd,
1 as dummy
from 
 (SELECT distinct 
codigo_sucursal as branch_office_cd ,nombre_sucursal as branch_office_name
FROM cdp_stg_dwh.stg_informeventas WHERE trim(codigo_ramo)='24') stg_informeventas
where branch_office_cd not in 
(select distinct branch_office_cd from cdp_dwh.dim_branch_office_t where src_sys_cd='penta')
) src
left outer join
(select 1 as dummy, max(dim_branch_office_key) as MAX_SID from cdp_dwh.dim_branch_office_t) LKP_MAXSID
on src.dummy = LKP_MAXSID.dummy
)
